      "writtenOn": "2018-09-28T23:01:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Probably not too important yet, but before we start using this seriously, IWBN to add os.exit(...) to this method and have a shared understanding between this code and Task Scheduler about which exit codes mean SUCCESS/FAILURE/MISHAP.",
