      "side": 1,
      "message": "IMO, if we make it easy to test built-in components, then it will probably be easy to test task drivers also. I think the biggest differences would be use of flags and, if we aren\u0027t mocking the execs, the time required to run the commands.",
      "parentUuid": "e30160c9_67d05617",
      "revId": "dea751d79cd1bdd5607b81eb9fd9a0ec6b19288e",
